Description: From Win8 on - the last 8 execution times are saved in the .pf file. With creation timestamp there are 9 execution times documented.
128 files on Win7 - 1024 from Win8 on. Older files are automatically deleted if 1024 is reached.
If a .pf is deleted - a new .pf file is generated with a new creation timestamp
Creation of a .pf does not imply successful execution
Indicator for the same program running from different paths
